## Edge Stacking

**Edges That Stack:**
- Weapon Technique (one per weapon type)
- Armor Adaptation (one per armor type)
- Tough (max 2 times total)
- Hardy (max 2 times total)
- Flow Harmony (max 3 times total)
- Skill Specialization (different applications)

**Edges That Don't Stack:**
- Quick Draw (once only)
- Combat Reflexes (once only)
- Fast Movement (once only)
- Precise Strike (once only)
- Defensive Fighter (once only)

